org.hibernate.ogm.jpa.impl

Class OgmEntityManagerFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.jpa.impl.OgmEntityManagerFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, javax.persistence.EntityManagerFactory, org.hibernate.jpa.HibernateEntityManagerFactory

    public class OgmEntityManagerFactory
extends Object
implements javax.persistence.EntityManagerFactory, org.hibernate.jpa.HibernateEntityManagerFactory
    An OGM EntityManagerFactory which delegates most work to the underlying ORM EntityManagerFactory. Note: Returns an OgmEntityManager to cope with query operations.
    Author:
    Emmanuel Bernard <emmanuel@hibernate.org>
